translate chinese laptopshop_e5210463:

    # "What should I search for?"
    "该搜什么呢？"

# game/Screens/laptop.rpy:35
translate chinese laptopshop_39579f17:

    # "I look at an internet auction site and find somebody selling Kendra's skateboard."
    "我浏览了一个网络拍卖网站，发现有人在卖肯德拉的滑板。"

# game/Screens/laptop.rpy:36
translate chinese laptopshop_64e8b184:

    # "$150? It's a lot of money, but it would make her happy."
    "150美元？虽然挺贵的，但这会让她开心。"

# game/Screens/laptop.rpy:39
translate chinese laptopshop_44c793eb:

    # "I buy the board. It'll take a few days to come in."
    "我买了那块滑板。大概需要几天才能到货。"

# game/Screens/laptop.rpy:43
translate chinese laptopshop_e547989c:

    # "I don't want to buy it right now. Maybe later."
    "我现在不想买。也许以后再说吧。"

# game/Screens/laptop.rpy:53
translate chinese buykendraboard_241d28dc:

    # "Although it wasn't really my fault that Kendra's board got broke, I think it would be nice if I bought her a new one."
    "虽然肯德拉的滑板坏了其实不完全是我的错，但我觉得给她买个新的会很贴心。"

# game/Screens/laptop.rpy:54
translate chinese buykendraboard_c80eccb5:

    # "I sit up the computer and open up an internet auction site where I find somebody selling the same skateboard."
    "我打开电脑，登录一个网络拍卖网站，发现有人在卖同一款滑板。"

# game/Screens/laptop.rpy:56
translate chinese buykendraboard_7de0f2fd:

    # "150!? That's a lot of money for a board with four wheels."
    "150！？一块带四个轮子的滑板，这价格也太高了吧。"

# game/Screens/laptop.rpy:57
translate chinese buykendraboard_8567cba3:

    # "But I have the money I guess, and it'd make her happy."
    "不过我手头倒是有这笔钱，而且能让她开心。"

# game/Screens/laptop.rpy:58
translate chinese buykendraboard_8acc8dc3:

    # "I think I'd like to make her happy."
    "我想，我还是想让她开心的。"

# game/Screens/laptop.rpy:59
translate chinese buykendraboard_31acde2b:

    # "I go ahead and buy the board. It'll take a few days to come in the mail."
    "我便下单买了那块滑板。邮寄过来大概需要几天时间。"

# game/Screens/laptop.rpy:78
translate chinese studyenglish_079e5bf3:

    # "And now it's time to get to school."
    "现在该去上学了。"

# game/Screens/laptop.rpy:79
translate chinese studyenglish_3f99fe4b:

    # "I rush downstairs and out to the car, then drive across town to get to class on time."
    "我匆匆跑下楼，冲到车里，然后开车穿过整个城区，赶在课前准时到达。"

# game/Screens/laptop.rpy:82
translate chinese studyenglish_5471bfe1:

    # "Then it's time to get ready for bed."
    "接着该准备睡觉了。"

