translate chinese soulsofwar_642c7d62:

    # "Adrian's not online right now. I don't really feel like playing without her. I should check later in the day."
    "艾德里安现在没上线。没有她我实在没心情玩。我等会儿再看看吧。"

# game/Screens/laptop.rpy:118
